</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="11.[151,1436,428,524]" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">
This is here recorded from 
<collectingCountry box="[481,520,428,452]" name="Fiji" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">Fiji</collectingCountry>
for the first time, from Taveuni from an unidentified host (Taveuni, Bouma, 
<date box="[151,281,463,487]" pageId="11" pageNumber="12" value="2009-07-23">
<number box="[151,180,463,487]" pageId="11" pageNumber="12" value="23.0">23</number>
.vii. 
<number box="[219,281,463,487]" pageId="11" pageNumber="12" value="2009.0">2009</number>
</date>
, C.J. Hodgson (
<collectionCode box="[460,551,463,487]" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">BMNH</collectionCode>
): 
<number box="[570,580,463,487]" pageId="11" pageNumber="12" value="1.0">1</number>
/ 
<number box="[591,601,463,487]" pageId="11" pageNumber="12" value="1.0">1</number>
adf.). 
<taxonomicName box="[672,823,465,488]" class="Insecta" family="Coccidae" genus="Kilifia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="12" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="acuminata">
<emphasis box="[672,823,465,488]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">K. acuminata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is a tropicopolitan species found throughout the tropical South Pacific and so its presence is not surprising.
</paragraph>
